{"tid":1587070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網絡戰 讓自由的空氣傳入大陸","createTime":"2019-09-22T09:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T10:11:13.000Z","uid":324194,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e79af1731cad6f2edf76398eee89c3002f02c5b4","tid":1587070,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"對面有幾十萬網軍點攻都攻唔入架啦 鬥唔過<br />\n<br />\n但我地係咪可以反過黎<br />\n諗下有冇計<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">令10.1 同國慶變成敏感詞</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">或者搞到微博微信 更多既字變成 *****、找不到符合条件</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國國內本來壓力就多，依家又有豬瘟，又愈黎愈多爆雷，銀行開出現倒閉潮連攞錢都可能係問題。<br />\n但壓力都總有個臨界點<br />\n既然改變唔撚到佢地，咁就推一把令佢地壓力錶繼續提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人就係冇野可以再失去既時候先識得反抗<br />\n有時有D人只能依靠一邊痛罵生活，一邊忍耐。<br />\n所以要令一堆字變成***，等佢地想打都打唔出、罵都罵唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b866f44af43b5b7ddb3a3205dd39ca7c2b408e01","tid":1587070,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"208e3f893462ec05fcba4de8b1bd14a6df1586f2","tid":1587070,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6126b944ef842598970de1de9007dded8f9b3ab","tid":1587070,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33132cb7493c1c364d0236bf936b010a7ed58447","tid":1587070,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"